worth every cent , penny , or other currency ! dj kid koala is probably one of the better djs today , in standards of both technique and creativity . his skill allows him to take basically every quote he would like and to mix it into the flow . texts and sounds as one , he manages to make it appear like a new , whole piece - which is exactly what a true dj supposed to do . by redefining the art of turntables , he has in this specific album all that 's needed - a bit of dark tracks , a bit of laughable samples ; and all in all , if you like the genre , this album is a must